--- [indian-med-africa] iter 29 | added=9 | Fri May 22 12:19:25 EDT 2026 ---
DONE: Lankan Manta Point added successfully

Added the Maldives' most-visited manta cleaning station to `north-male-atoll-maldives` (which previously had only 2 sites). Eastern outer reef of Lankanfinolhu, three coral bommies at 10–18 m acting as fixed cleaning stations, peak Aug–Nov on the southwest monsoon. Hero image left null — no Lankan-specific underwater photo exists on Wikimedia Commons, and per the rules a generic Maldives manta would be misleading.

Sources used:
- [Lankan Manta Point - SSI Dive Guide](https://www.divessi.com/en/mydiveguide/divesite/lankan-manta-point-maldives-678063)
- [Manta Point Maldives - Liveaboard.com](https://www.liveaboard.com/diving/article/manta-point-maldives)
