Added the MS Zenobia (172m Ro-Ro ferry that capsized off Larnaca in 1980, lies on her port side 16–42m) along with a new `larnaca-cyprus` location entry. Hero image is the iconic propeller shot from Wikimedia Commons (4000×3000, CC-BY 2.0). One of the most-cited wreck dives in the Mediterranean and our first Cyprus site.

